## Quality Assurance Workflow Integration (Integrated)
**VALIDATE CONTINUOUSLY:** Ensure quality throughout content lifecycle

### 1. Commit-Time Quality Gates
**Pre-Commit Validation:**

#### Automated Quality Checks
**Git Hook Integration:**
```bash
# Pre-commit quality validation
#!/bin/bash
echo "Running quality checks..."

# YAML validation
if ! yamllint content/*.mdc; then
    echo "❌ YAML validation failed"
    exit 1
fi

# Markdown validation
if ! markdownlint content/*.mdc; then
    echo "❌ Markdown validation failed"
    exit 1
fi

# Cross-reference validation
if ! validate-references content/*.mdc; then
    echo "❌ Cross-reference validation failed"
    exit 1
fi

echo "✅ All quality checks passed"
```

